  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[When Digivolving] You may reveal the top 3 cards of your
    deck. For each of your opponent's Digimon, you may play 1 Digimon card with [Mamemon]
    in its name and a memory cost of 10 or less among the revealed cards without
    paying its memory cost. Trash the remaining cards.[All Turns] While you have
    another Digimon with [Mamemon] in its name in play, this Digimon gains \uFF1CSecurity
    Attack +1\uFF1E. (This Digimon checks 1 additional security card.)"
